{"componentChunkName":"component---src-layouts-blog-post-layout-js","path":"/blog/search-bar-always-visible-tutorial","result":{"pageContext":{"id":1974,"date":"2022-12-02T23:41:27","date_gmt":"2022-12-02T23:41:27","guid":{"rendered":"https://www.ezfy.club/?p=1974"},"modified":"2022-12-02T23:52:46","modified_gmt":"2022-12-02T23:52:46","slug":"search-bar-always-visible-tutorial","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https://www.ezfy.club/search-bar-always-visible-tutorial/","title":{"rendered":"Make the search bar always visible on all themes (desktop and mobile)"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>All Shopify free themes have access to a search functionality: a magnifying glass shaped search icon that when clicked opens a search bar, where you can then type whatever you&#8217;re looking for and any matching results among your store&#8217;s products will be shown to you . While a great tool for any store or page in the web, having to click the search icon before revealing the search bar is one click too much and a step that could simply be skipped. <br><br>Using this tutorial you&#8217;ll learn not only how to make the search bar permanently visible and accessible on desktop but also on mobile regardless of the device you&#8217;re using, using only copy and pasted code that will work on all free themes.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"NoticeBox NoticeBox--info\"><p>This tutorial is compatible with all Shopify&#8217;s official free themes: <b>Dawn, Refresh, Colorblock, Taste, Ride, Studio, Crave, Origina, Publisher, Sense &amp; Craft.</b></p></div>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-making-a-backup-of-your-theme\">Making a backup of your theme</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Before diving into the tutorial make sure you download the theme, so in case you face any issues you can easily revert back.<br><br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1514\" height=\"481\" class=\"wp-image-503\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123.png 1514w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-600x191.png 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-1200x381.png 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-768x244.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1514px) 100vw, 1514px\" /></p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-step-by-step\">Step by step</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Open your Shopify admin and click <strong>Online Store &gt; Themes &gt; Actions &gt; Edit Code &gt; Snippets &gt; Add a new snippet</strong><br><br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1261\" height=\"407\" class=\"wp-image-1917\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_3.png\" alt=\"Opening code editor in the Dawn theme\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_3.png 1261w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_3-850x274.png 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_3-1200x387.png 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_3-768x248.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1261px) 100vw, 1261px\" /><br></li><li>A popup window will appear prompting you to name the new snippet file. Paste or type in the following, exactly as it is:<br><br><strong>ezfy-header-search</strong><br><br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1084\" height=\"456\" class=\"wp-image-1995\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_6.png\" alt=\"Creating the ezfy-header-search.liquid snippet file in the code editor\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_6.png 1084w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_6-850x358.png 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_6-768x323.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1084px) 100vw, 1084px\" /><br></li><li>In the new file you just created, paste the following code:<br><br>[gist]a76cbdeef2f127006ff41570a47d399b[gist]<br><br>Then click the green &#8220;save&#8221; button and move on to the next step.<br><br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1027\" height=\"539\" class=\"wp-image-1998\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_7.png\" alt=\"Saving the ezfy-header-search.liquid snippet\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_7.png 1027w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_7-850x446.png 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_7-768x403.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1027px) 100vw, 1027px\" /><br></li><li>Next open the Sections folder in the menu to the left and click the <strong>header.liquid</strong> file to open it. <br><br>In it, press <strong>CTRL + F</strong> (or <strong>CMD + F</strong> on <strong>Mac</strong>) to open the search bar and paste in the following:<br><br><code>&lt;details-modal class=\"header__search\"</code>&gt;<br><br>Click &#8220;next&#8221; and you&#8217;ll be taken to the location of the first instance of the search icon in the file. Immediately <strong><em>above </em></strong>it paste the following code:<br><br><code>{% include 'ezfy-header-search', search_type: \"desktop\" %}</code><br><br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1114\" height=\"541\" class=\"wp-image-2001\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_8.png\" alt=\"Finding the location of the header__search in the header.liquid file\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_8.png 1114w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_8-850x413.png 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_8-768x373.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1114px) 100vw, 1114px\" /><br><br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"850\" height=\"509\" class=\"wp-image-2003\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_9.png\" alt=\"Adding the &quot;include&quot; liquid tag in the header.liquid file\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_9.png 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_9-768x460.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 850px) 100vw, 850px\" /><br></li><li>Repeat the search from step 4 but this time click &#8220;next&#8221; twice to find the second and final instance of the search icon deeper down into the file. Again right <strong><em>above </em></strong>it, paste the following:<br><br><code>{%- if section.settings.logo_position != 'top-center' -%}<br>{% include 'ezfy-header-search', search_type: 'desktop' %}<br>{%- endif -%}</code><br><br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"590\" height=\"524\" class=\"wp-image-2005\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_10.png\" alt=\"Finding the location of the header__search in the header.liquid file\"><br><br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"627\" height=\"548\" class=\"wp-image-2007\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_11.png\" alt=\"Adding the &quot;include&quot; liquid tag in the header.liquid file\"><br></li><li>Finally, open the search bar a third time and search for the following:<br><br><code>&lt;/header&gt;</code><br><br>Right <strong><em>below </em></strong>that line, paste the following:<br><br><code>{% include 'ezfy-header-search', search_type: 'mobile' %}</code><br><br>And you&#8217;re done! Don&#8217;t forget to click the &#8220;save&#8221; button on the top right of the screen.<br><br> <img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"499\" height=\"529\" class=\"wp-image-2010\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_12.png\" alt=\"Finding the header closing tag in the header.liquid file\"><br><br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1021\" height=\"536\" class=\"wp-image-2012\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_13.png\" alt=\"Saving the header.liquid file\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_13.png 1021w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_13-850x446.png 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_13-768x403.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1021px) 100vw, 1021px\" /></li></ol>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-conclusion\">Conclusion</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>You and your clients can now search your store more easily with a single click!<br><br>Before:<br><br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1340\" height=\"420\" class=\"wp-image-2015\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_15.png\" alt=\"Default search icon in Dawn theme\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_15.png 1340w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_15-850x266.png 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_15-1200x376.png 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_15-768x241.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1340px) 100vw, 1340px\" /><br><br>After:<br><br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1339\" height=\"408\" class=\"wp-image-2017\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_14.png\" alt=\"Always visible search bar in Dawn theme\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_14.png 1339w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_14-850x259.png 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_14-1200x366.png 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_14-768x234.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1339px) 100vw, 1339px\" /><br><br>It works regardless of the logo position you have selected:<br><br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1344\" height=\"453\" class=\"wp-image-2020\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_16.png\" alt=\"Always visible search bar in Dawn theme\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_16.png 1344w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_16-850x286.png 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_16-1200x404.png 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_16-768x259.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1344px) 100vw, 1344px\" /><br><br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1344\" height=\"432\" class=\"wp-image-2022\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_17.png\" alt=\"Always visible search bar in Dawn theme\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_17.png 1344w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_17-850x273.png 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_17-1200x386.png 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_17-768x247.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1344px) 100vw, 1344px\" /><br><br>And also on mobile:<br><br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"395\" height=\"399\" class=\"wp-image-2024\" style=\"width: 1600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_18.png\" alt=\"Always visible search bar in Dawn theme, mobile\"><br><br>If you found any issues during or you&#8217;d like your search bar to be customized further, just send us an email at <strong>ezfycode@gmail.com</strong> and we&#8217;ll be ready provide further guidance and offer a quote. </p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-you-may-also-like\">You may also like</h3>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/blog/add-slideshow-shopify-no-apps\">&#8211; How to make slideshow images stop cutting off</a><br><a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/blog/how-to-disable-right-click-image-and-text-copying-without-apps\">&#8211; Disable right click, image and text copying and improve your store&#8217;s security</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Make it so the search bar is always visible without the need for clicking the search icon every time. Works on all free themes including Dawn.</p>\n","protected":false},"author":5,"featured_media":2037,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[9],"tags":[655,626,657,435,776,773,663,649,652,646,660],"acf":[],"image_alt":"","featured_image_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/studio-slider-3-2-850x478.png","featured_image_small_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/studio-slider-3-2-200x200.png","featured_image_large_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/studio-slider-3-2-1200x675.png","categories_names":["Blog"],"tag_names":["Colorblock Theme","Craft Theme","Crave Theme","Dawn Theme","origin theme","publisher theme","Refresh theme","Ride theme","Sense Theme","Studio Theme","Taste theme"],"featured_image_url":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/studio-slider-3-2.png","featured_image_url_alt":"Make the search bar always visible on all themes blog post image","_links":{"self":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/1974"}],"collection":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/types/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/users/5"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/comments?post=1974"}],"version-history":[{"count":10,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/1974/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":2042,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/1974/revisions/2042"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/media/2037"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/media?parent=1974"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/categories?post=1974"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/tags?post=1974"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https://api.w.org/{rel}","templated":true}]}}},"staticQueryHashes":["330429198"]}